WEBVTT

00:03:59.889 --> 00:04:01.610
that I wanted to go to law school.

00:04:02.482 --> 00:04:04.816
Grandma didn't pause.
She didn't skip a beat.

00:04:04.840 --> 00:04:07.759
She said to me, "Lawyer is liar."

00:04:08.744 --> 00:04:11.735
(Laughter)

00:04:11.759 --> 00:04:13.902
That was discouraging.

00:04:13.926 --> 00:04:17.219
(Laughter)

00:04:17.243 --> 00:04:18.905
But grandma's right, in a way.

00:04:18.929 --> 00:04:22.286
Something about law
and lawyers has gone wrong.

00:04:23.194 --> 00:04:27.249
We lawyers are usually
expensive, first of all,

00:04:27.273 --> 00:04:30.074
and we tend to focus
on formal court channels